name: Ice Maker Assembly
description: Replacement ice maker assembly for Whirlpool, KitchenAid, and Maytag refrigerators. Complete unit includes housing, motor, and ejector blade.
installation_steps:
1. Turn off refrigerator and water supply
2. Remove ice bin and mounting screws
3. Disconnect wiring harness
4. Remove old ice maker
5. Install new ice maker and reconnect wiring
6. Secure with mounting screws
7. Turn on water supply and power

name: Water Inlet Valve
description: Water inlet valve controls water flow to ice maker and water dispenser. Fits Whirlpool and Kenmore refrigerators.

name: Door Gasket Seal
description: Magnetic door gasket creates airtight seal. Prevents cold air loss. Universal fit for most refrigerator models.

name: Dishwasher Spray Arm
description: Lower spray arm assembly for dishwashers. Includes spray jets and mounting hub. Ensures proper water distribution.

name: Dishwasher Door Latch
description: Door latch and handle assembly. Secures dishwasher door during operation. Includes strike and catch mechanism.

name: Dishwasher Heating Element
description: Heating element for drying cycle. 1200W high-efficiency element. Compatible with Whirlpool and KitchenAid models.

name: Refrigerator Water Filter
description: Premium water filter reduces contaminants including lead, chlorine, and pharmaceuticals. 6-month filter life.

name: Evaporator Fan Motor
description: Evaporator fan motor circulates cold air throughout refrigerator. Includes fan blade and mounting bracket.

name: Dishwasher Drain Pump
description: Drain pump removes water from dishwasher tub. High-capacity motor ensures complete drainage.

name: Temperature Control Thermostat
description: Electronic temperature control for refrigerator. Precise temperature regulation with digital display.
